    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00037",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "岳胜"
      ],
      "text": "岂敢无礼！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00038",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "哇呀……恁兄弟奉着哥哥将令，巡查界河，一路平安无事，俺今特来交令。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00039",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延昭"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟多有辛苦。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00040",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "好说。方才那一小校说，元帅与岳将军在后帐议论紧急军情，用俺不着，叫俺回避，俺故此吓他。",
      "text_length": 43
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00041",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延昭"
      ],
      "text": "此话是我对他说的。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00042",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "岳胜"
      ],
      "text": "果有此话。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00043",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀，果有此话？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00044",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延昭"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟，我这里用你不着，你自回避。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00045",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "用哪个不着？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
