      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀，哥呀！你今番就是杀了俺，也是偏不回避的。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00050",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延昭"
      ],
      "text": "岳贤弟，你看孟良哪知我的心事来。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00051",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "岳胜"
      ],
      "text": "正是。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00052",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "呀！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00053",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "红绣鞋",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "往常时，无我来不喜欢说话，今日个，见俺来便低着头无语使这嗟呀！",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00054",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "哥！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
