        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "莫不是大辽兵马前来蹅踏，俺与你火速地便去争杀。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00070",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "岳胜"
      ],
      "text": "不是。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00071",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 71,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "石榴花",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "莫不是王枢密搬弄着、搬弄着宋官家，俺与你急忙备马便去京华。",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00072",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 72,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "岳胜"
      ],
      "text": "不是。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00073",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 73,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀是了。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00074",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 74,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "石榴花",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "莫不是佘太君定有人便相欺压，",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00075",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 75,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延昭"
      ],
      "text": "孟贤弟，我的老母谁敢欺压！",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00076",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 76,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "吖咳，着啊！量他们确也不敢！",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00077",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 77,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "石榴花",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "则除非赵玄坛威力无加，才敢把虎头儿须来抓。俺与你亲自把贼拿。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00078",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 78,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延昭"
      ],
      "text": "孟贤弟，我要取一物，他那里兵多将广，只怕你一人取他不来。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00079",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 79,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "那厮他！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00080",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 80,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "斗鹌鹑",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "又不是布雾的蚩尤，又不是飞天、飞天的夜叉。那厮便躲在云中，藏在了藏在了地下。俺可也翻过了乾坤，若见他，说那厮能变化。",
      "text_length": 58
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00081",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 81,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "吼一吼！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00082",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 82,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "斗鹌鹑",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "骨碌碌海沸山崩，觑一觑，觑一觑天摧地塌。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00083",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 83,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延昭"
      ],
      "text": "孟贤弟，量你也猜不着。待愚兄对你说了吧。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00084",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 84,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "我的哥，请讲，请讲！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00085",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 85,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延昭"
      ],
      "text": "昨夜偶得一梦，梦得我父老元戎托梦于我，说被番兵困在虎口交牙峪，只困得内无粮草，外无救兵，我父差七郎兄弟前到雄关搬兵求救，不想被潘仁美乱箭射死！",
      "text_length": 71
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00086",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 86,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "哇呀……我的哥，请讲，请讲！",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00087",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 87,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延昭"
      ],
      "text": "那时我父盼兵不到，盼子不归，无奈碰死在李陵碑下。尸骨被番兵盗去，吊在幽州昊天塔上，每日用一百个小番，各射一箭，名曰百箭会。",
      "text_length": 61
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00088",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 88,
      "seq_in_scene": 88,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "哇呀……请讲，请讲！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00089",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 89,
      "seq_in_scene": 89,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延昭"
      ],
      "text": "那时我父幽魂疼痛难忍，来在三关渡口，托我一梦，叫我盗取爹爹骨殖而归。是我无计可施，故此伤感吓。",
      "text_length": 47
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00090",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 90,
      "seq_in_scene": 90,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "我的哥，我想这件事，别人去不得，恁兄弟我倒也去得。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00091",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 91,
      "seq_in_scene": 91,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延昭"
      ],
      "text": "你去不得。你……",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00092",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 92,
      "seq_in_scene": 92,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "啊……",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00093",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 93,
      "seq_in_scene": 93,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "岳胜"
      ],
      "text": "不能！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00094",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 94,
      "seq_in_scene": 94,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00095",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 95,
      "seq_in_scene": 95,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "上小楼",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "凭着俺烧天火把，说什么经忏佛法。大踏步踹入僧房，拿住和尚，揝定袈裟。性气差，忿怒发，拖离禅榻，",
      "text_length": 47
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00096",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 96,
      "seq_in_scene": 96,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "滴溜溜噗！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00097",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 97,
      "seq_in_scene": 97,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "上小楼",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "脑袋儿殿前阶下。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00098",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 98,
      "seq_in_scene": 98,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延昭"
      ],
      "text": "孟贤弟，你若拿住那厮便怎样？",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00099",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 99,
      "seq_in_scene": 99,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "我若拿住他！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00100",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 100,
      "seq_in_scene": 100,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "上小楼",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "胸脯上脚去蹬，面门上把来抓。凭着俺腰下宣斧，乞抽扢叉、斫他鼻凹。恶菩萨、狠那吒，金刚答话，我直着释迦佛也整理不下。",
      "text_length": 57
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00101",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 101,
      "seq_in_scene": 101,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延昭"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟执意要去，可带多少人马？",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00102",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 102,
      "seq_in_scene": 102,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "我的哥。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00103",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 103,
      "seq_in_scene": 103,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "尾声",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "凭着俺火轮儿左手拿，宣花斧右手杀。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00104",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 104,
      "seq_in_scene": 104,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "摇一摇，晃一晃，震动了千层琉璃瓦！",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00105",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 105,
      "seq_in_scene": 105,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "尾声",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "俺可也推倒玲珑舍利塔！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00106",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 106,
      "seq_in_scene": 106,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟良"
      ],
      "text": "我的哥请。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00107",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 107,
      "seq_in_scene": 107,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "孟良下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00108",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 108,
      "seq_in_scene": 108,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "岳胜"
      ],
      "text": "孟良此去必然成功。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00109",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 109,
      "seq_in_scene": 109,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延昭"
      ],
      "text": "正是：",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00110",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 110,
      "seq_in_scene": 110,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延昭"
      ],
      "text": "岳贤弟紧守营盘，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00111",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 111,
      "seq_in_scene": 111,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "岳胜"
      ],
      "text": "孟火星谁敢挡拦。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00112",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 112,
      "seq_in_scene": 112,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延昭"
      ],
      "text": "众头领休离汛地，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901103_e00113",
      "play_id": "70901103",
      "scene_id": "70901103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 113,
      "seq_in_scene": 113,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "同念",
      "speakers": [
        "岳胜",
        "杨延昭"
      ],
      "text": "取骨殖早回三关。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
